backwards in the central Bamyan province after making a major gain
over the weekend, reports monitored here said Monday.
</P>
<P>
The Taliban captured the Punjab district at the weekend with
heavy casualties from the Hezb-e-Wahdat led by Kharim Khalili, the
reports quoted Taliban-controlled Radio Shariat as saying.
</P>
<P>
