<DOCNO> XIE19980928.0046 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-28 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> People's Daily Editorial to Hail Victory of Anti-Flood Campaign </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 28 (Xinhua) -- China's leading newspaper
"People's Daily" will carry an editorial tomorrow hailing the
victory of the just-concluded national anti-flood and rescue
operation and commending those who made outstanding contributions
to the flood-fighting campaign this year.
</P>
<P>
Titled "Studying Flood-fighting Models and Promoting
Flood-fighting Spirit," the editorial sends a lofty salute to
those who made prominent contributions in the campaign and
expresses thanks to those who made donations for flood relief.
</P>
<P>
Echoing the grand national conference on review and
commendation of the flood-fighting and disaster-relief endeavor
held in Beijing on Monday, the editorial terms the victory, in the
final analysis, a victory of the people, and says the people are
the mainstay and motive power pushing ahead the development of
history.
</P>
<P>
However, those leading the people forward and influencing them
spiritually are heroes and models among them, the editorial points
out, saying that they are all the glory of the Party, the pride of
the people, and the deserving national heroes.
</P>
<P>
The editorial says that learning from these heroes and models
requires learning their unselfish dedication, their perseverance
in times of emergency, and their patriotic and collective spirit
centering on the national interests and the people's interests.
</P>
<P>
The flood-fighting spirit is a reflection of the strength to
fight against difficulty and strive for success in the new
circumstance, it says.
</P>
<P>
In reality, the editorial says, in order to learn from the
flood-fighting heroes and models, the people should unite closely
around the Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin as the core,
hold high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, and forge
ahead along the route of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics to realize the great goal in the next century.
</P>
</TEXT>
