<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin On Overall National Strength (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 28 (Xinhua) -- A national spirit is an
important measurement of a country's overall national strength,
the Chinese president Jiang Zemin stressed here today.
</P>
<P>
A nation or a country would lose its soul, cohesion and
vitality without a spirit to sustain it, Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
The overall national strength is embodied mainly in its
economic and technical level. This material strength is the basis
while the spiritual strength, such as the national spirit and
cohesion, is also an important part of the overall national
strength, and is indispensable as well, he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made this remark at today's National Conference on Review
and Commendation of Flood Fighting and Disaster Relief Endeavor.
</P>
<P>
He said, in the battle against the floods, our nation and our
people demonstrated a lofty spirit: the spirit of unity and
solidarity, working with one mind and one will; the spirit of
tenacity and fortitude, fearing no difficulties and daring to win
victory. This spirit prevailed in the fight against the floods,
and that is the great flood-fighting spirit.
</P>
<P>
He said, the great unity of will displayed in fighting the
floods gave full expression to the strong cohesion of the Chinese
people. From the thousand-li-long dykes to the capital Beijing,
from the Yangtze River to the Great Wall, from the coastal cities
and provinces to the border and ethnic minorities inhabited
areas, the people of the whole country, both at the flood
fighting forefront and in the rear areas, worked in close
coordination in a concerted effort. Our men and women, old and
young, pooled their strength together.
</P>
<P>
He said, the more critical the juncture of revolution,
construction and reform is, the more clearly the Chinese people
would display such extraordinary spirit of cohesion. With such
cohesion, we will be forever invincible.
</P>
<P>
Putting up a tenacious struggle in defiance of difficulties
embodies the revolutionary heroism of the Chinese people. In this
great struggle, many heroes who charged ahead regardless of their
personal safety or even sacrificed their lives emerged. With the
inspiration of this revolutionary heroism, the Chinese people will
forever stand firm in the family of nations.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19980928.0151 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-28 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin On Overall National Strength (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
He said, persistence and daring to win reflect the strong will
and confidence of the Chinese people. The more dangerous the
situations grew, the more indomitable the soldiers and civilians
became with their extraordinary courage and will. With this
spirit, no difficulty was insurmountable for them.
</P>
<P>
Jiang Zemin pointed out that according to the Marxist
materialist dialectics, under certain conditions, the spiritual
strength may be transformed into material strength. Powerful
spiritual strength may not only promote the development of
material and technical strength, but also enable certain material
and technical strength to play a bigger role.
</P>
<P>
He said, the Chinese nation has a great national spirit of its
own. This spirit, which has evolved in the course of several
thousand years, is broad, profound and deeply-rooted. It is an
important part and parcel of the life of the Chinese nation.
Over the past five thousand years, the Chinese nation has
stiffened its belief and will through untold sufferings and
difficulties, opened up the land, built up this beautiful country
and created a splendid Chinese civilization, thus making an
indelible contribution to the progress of human civilization.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said, the flood-fighting spirit is a crystallization of
patriotism, collectivism, the socialist spirit, the socialist
moral standards and the glorious tradition and fine working style
of our Party and army. It represents a new development of the
national spirit of the Chinese nation in modern time.
</P>
<P>
He said, like the revolutionary spirit consistently promoted by
the Party and the pioneering spirit of the new era, the
flood-fighting spirit is a valuable spiritual asset of our
people, which should be inherited and upheld by our future
generations and should serve to inspire our cadres and people to
forge ahead from one victory to another. 
</P>
</TEXT>
