floods, with its tremendous impact, is encouraging and impelling
the people in the disaster areas to overcome all difficulties in
their endeavor to resume production and rebuild their homes, and
is inspiring and encouraging the entire Chinese people to go all
out to fulfill their strategic tasks for trans-century development.
</P>
<P>
