</P>
<P>
Scarlet Light's son, Richard, is a 1.95 meter freshman, and
finding affordable size 16 shoes in California, has been an
almost impossible task for her.
</P>
<P>
After calling several NBA teams, Scarlet reached the Clippers,
who were willing to part with a pair of sneakers. A new pair of
red and white, size 16 Reeboks showed up at the Light's door
yesterday.
</P>
<P>
