basketball only for recreation.
</P>
<P>
Unitl the shoes arrived, Light had to squeeze into a pair of
size 14 basketball shoes, which he has been wearing for several
months.
</P>
<P>
"He is huge, and I want him to feel halfway comfortable at
school," Scarlet Light said. 
